par double eagle at the par-5 second hole to take a two-shot
lead during the final round of the Masters Tournament.  It was the first double eagle at the second hole in the
tournament and the fourth at any hole in the eventâ€™s 76-year
history.  Oosthuizen, the 2010 British Open champion, is 10-under.
